Boiss.
</taxonomicName>
but differs in its smaller leaves with a denser indumentum composed of long (ca 
<quantity id="3D609B3477355B68D93310BCFB43938C" box="[1091,1161,735,761]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="74" unit="mm" value="1.0">1 mm</quantity>
) trichomes, cyathial glands with digitate appendages and pubescent ovary /fruit.
</paragraph>
